{
  "page": "Maiden's Fancy",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Maiden's Fancy</b></i> was the name of a small ship captained by <a href=\"/index.php/Elissa_Farman\" title=\"Elissa Farman\">Elissa Farman</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maiden%27s_Fancy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Farman\" title=\"Marq Farman\">Marq Farman</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a> died in <a href=\"/index.php/50_AC\" title=\"50 AC\">50&#160;AC</a>, his eldest son <a href=\"/index.php/Franklyn_Farman\" title=\"Franklyn Farman\">Franklyn Farman</a> became the new <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>. He ordered <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Aenys I)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>, who had been a guest of his late father, to leave <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a>. Rhaena and her companions left on the <i>Maiden's Fancy</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maiden%27s_Fancy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Year of the Three Brides - 49 AC.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404044125\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.044 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 226/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8628/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 774/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 378/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1045/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.64 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   39.213      1 -total\n 71.52%   28.044      1 Template:Italic_title\n 14.14%    5.545      2 Template:Ref\n 10.05%    3.942      1 Template:Date\n  9.40%    3.687      2 Template:Ref/core\n  3.54%    1.389      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache 